    About this item

    • PROFESSIONAL PHOTO AND VIDEO PERFORMANCE: 16 megapixel Micro Four Thirds sensor with no low pass filter to confidently capture sharp images with a high dynamic range and artifact free performance; WiFi enabled
    • 4K VIDEO CAPTURE: 4K QHD video recording (3840 x 2160) with three 4K Ultra HD capture at 25p and Full HD ( 1920 * 1080 ) at 50p
    • 4K PHOTO MODE : 8MP PHOTO BURST MODE at 30 fps, extracts individual high resolution images from 4K Ultra HD video filmed at 30 frames per second to capture split second moments
    • INTUITIVE CONTROLS: Easily control aperture and shutter settings with the front and rear dials while making white balance and ISO adjustments on the fly; Assign favorite settings to any of the six function buttons (six on body, five on menu)
    • HIGH RESOLUTION VIEWFINDER AND LCD DISPLAY: High resolution (2,360K dot) OLED Live View Finder and rear touch enabled 3 inch tilt/swivel LCD display (1,040 dot) are clear even in bright sunlight, Image sensor size 17.3 x 13.0 mm (in 4:3 aspect ratio)
    • CONNECTIVITY AND PORTS: 3.5mm external mic port, 2.5mm remote port, USB 2.0 and micro HDMI Type D; Compatible with newer UHS I/UHS II SDXC/SDHC SD cards capable of storing high resolution 4K videos
    • Manufacturer Detail: Panasonic AVC Networks Xiamen Co. Ltd., Hi-Tech Industrial Development Zone, Xiamen, Fujian, China

    What is in the box?

  • 1N Camera body, 1N Hot Shoe Cover, 1N Body Cap, 1N Battery Pack, 1N Battery Charger, 1N USB Connection Cable, 1N Shoulder Strap, 1N DVD, 1N AC Cable, 1N Lens Hood, 1N Lens Cap, 1N Lens Rear Cap, 1N Operating Instructions
  • Camera Body & Lens

    • From the manufacturer

    See more

    .

    Perfect Moment

    Special moments you want to remember can occur at any time and should be captured in the best resolution possible . Now Panasonic's 4K technology is available for everyone. With the introduction of new DMC-G7, you will be able to record video in 4K (upto QFHD: 3840*2160 pixels, 25fps, 100Mbits/s)

    Focus on the Moment

    Be ready to grab the next sudden shutter opportunity adding Depth from Defocus (DFD) Auto Focus (AF) technology to contrast AF has achieved both higher precision and greater speed .

    4K Video

    Whether you are watching movie or editing a videos, 4K delivers far more intense viewing experience than you have seen before. Its native resolution 3840*2160, pixels is four time larger than Full HD . Resulting in a much higher level of detail. Even if you export your footage filmed in 4K to a full HD TV, The videos will have even better definition and crisper details

    See more

    .

    High Speed Auto Focusing with FHD Technology

    Capture even the fastest moving action thanks to Panasonic Depth From Defocus (DFD) Auo Focus (AF) Technology. This new technology instantly calculates distance between the items inside the frame and drives the focus of the lens in one fast, continous movement. The new system results in AF Speeds upto 0.007 seconds and a burst shooting speed with AFC of 6 frames per second .

    Focusing in Low light Conditions - Star Light AF

    Low light AF makes it possible to focus subjects more precisely in -4EV low light situation, like moonlight with no other light source.Furthermore the starlight AF let you shoot a star in the night sky with auto focus by accurate calculation of the contrast value in a smaller AF zone.

    High Image Quality Even in Low Light Condition

    The 16 megapixel Digital live MOS Sensor in combination with the Venus Engine provides both: High quality image capture and high speed signal processing . The superior noise reduction system enables crisp images even in low light conditions up to ISO 25600. The venus Engine also exels in diffraction compensation to make images crisp and clear even when shooting a small aperture.

    See more

    .

    Perfect Sight & Framing

    The DMC-G7 comes with a high resolution OLED Live View Finder which allows high visibility thanks a ton to a 10,0000:1 contrast and perfect framing even under direct sunlight condition. Also with all your settings displayed right in front of your eye, your pictures will always come out exactly how you want them . A rear monitor also features high visibility even for sunny outdoor shooting. And, the tilt touch display give you the freedom to find unusual prespectives while maintaining easy operation and full image control.

    Unwire your Creativity via Wi-fi

    The connectivity features expands the usability of this camera in many ways.The camera can be controlled by using the "Panasonic Image App'' enabling you to view the image, set the focus, release the shutter from a distance or review photographs on the large screen .

    4K photo - Capture the Perfect Moment

    Using the high resolution of 4k, Panasonic DMC-G7GW camera introduces the new 4K Photo Function which allows you to extract individual frames from a video sequence (filmed at 30 frame per second) to caputre those magical moments that only occur at a split second.

    See more
